                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18150405-19-off102 t18150405-19-cd103"></join>, and stealing therein four waistcoats, value 12 s. a pair of breeches, value 1 l. a shawl value 16 s. a coat, value 1 l. 4 s. and a remnant of patent cord, value 1 s.
            </rs> his property.</p>
