            ; 
               <persName id="t18150405-19-person271">
                  Charles 
                  Beard
               <interp inst="t18150405-19-person271" type="surname" value="Beard"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18150405-19-person271" type="given" value="Charles"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18150405-19-person271" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
             works for my brother, he is a wood-chopper.</p>
               <p>
