             SENIOR. Q. Do you know 
               <persName id="t18150405-19-person273">
                  Charles 
                  Beard
               <interp inst="t18150405-19-person273" type="surname" value="Beard"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18150405-19-person273" type="given" value="Charles"></interp>
