                  </persName>
             brought me a bundle tied up in a white handkerchief, two waistcoats, and one pair of breeches; he told me to take care of them.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18150405-19-person275">
                  THOMAS 
                  THWAITES
               <interp inst="t18150405-19-person275" type="surname" value="THWAITES"></interp>
