            . I am shopman to Mr. Harris, pawnbroker. On the morning of the 18th of February, 
               <persName id="t18150405-19-person276">
                  Sarah 
                  Britt
               <interp inst="t18150405-19-person276" type="surname" value="Britt"></interp>
